Afro Rock singer, Sam Miracle has concluded plans to hold a live concert in the United States in April. Sam Miracle’s Afro Rock concert is scheduled to hold on April 11 at Murphy Mansion, in Dallas. King Sam Miracle won the award for Best Afro Rock Musician of The Year at the maiden edition of All Colour Awards 2019 in Lagos. Miracle also revealed that there are plans to have a grand concert in Nigeria in May after the US concert. Miracle’s latest musical effort, ‘Supernatural Blessing’ is proof of his brilliance in Afro rock music. According to inside sources, the musical concert in the United States will bring together thousands of music lovers across the country.